  The CUSTOM RESTRICTED LICENSE is designed to protect the creator’s
exclusive control over their work. Unlike free or open-source licenses,
this license intentionally prohibits use, modification, redistribution,
and hosting of the software without explicit written permission.

  In contrast to licenses that encourage sharing, modification, or
collaboration, this license ensures that the original author maintains
full ownership rights. Viewing the source code does *not* grant permission
to run, use, modify, copy, distribute, or deploy it in any personal,
educational, commercial, or research capacity.

  The intent of this license is to allow publication of source code for
reference, archival, demonstration, or verification purposes, while
preventing unauthorized use in any form.

  If you wish to use the Software in any way beyond reading it, you
must obtain express written permission from the copyright holder.


